- Sockets:
  . SO_ATTACH_REUSEPORT_CBPF (Linux only).
  . TCP_QUICKACK (Linux only).
  . IP_DONTFRAG (FreeBSD only).
  . IP_MTU_DISCOVER (Linux only).
  . IP_PMTUDISC_DO (Linux only).
  . IP_PMTUDISC_DONT (Linux only).
